"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:10.6.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">10.6.1</span> 标题：香、香水（perfumes）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：רקח, רֶקַח, רֹקַח, רַקָּח, רִקֻּחַ, מִרְקַחַת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：raqach（动词）, reqach, roqach, riquach, mirqachath)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:25\">EXO 30:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:25\">EXO 30:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:25\">EXO 30:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:35\">EXO 30:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:35\">EXO 30:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:29\">EXO 37:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:13\">1SA 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:30\">1CH 9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:30\">1CH 9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:14\">2CH 16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:14\">2CH 16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:8\">NEH 3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:1\">ECC 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:2\">SNG 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:9\">ISA 57:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：שֶׁמֶן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：shemen)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:2\">2SA 14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:9\">PRO 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:1\">ECC 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:8\">ECC 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:1\">ECC 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:3\">SNG 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:3\">SNG 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:10\">SNG 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:9\">ISA 57:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:3\">ISA 61:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:9\">EZK 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:15\">MIC 6:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἤδυσμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：ēdusma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/EsthGr4:17\">ESG 4:17</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>一般来说，香水是把芬芳的香料混合在乳油里面制成的，可用来掩盖难闻的气味，例如汗臭、腐烂的尸体，甚至是祭祀时屠杀祭牲的血腥味。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯来文动词<em>raqach</em> 意为“混合、复合”，而希伯来文<em>shemen</em> 意指“油”。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
